sections.Trivia:
- Yukiko's cellphone photo along with Yusaku and baby Shinichi is from The Ten Planets in the Night Sky.
- The crashed car is a brilliant metallic blue 2000 Suzuki Kei [HN11S].
- The names of the suspects come from beaches[2]:
- Shigekatsu Fukumizu (福水 繁克) comes from Zushi Beach (逗子海水浴場), Kanagawa Prefecture;
- Yasue Kitamori (北森 靖絵) comes from Moriya Beach (守谷海水浴場), Chiba Prefecture;
- Raiya Oami (大網 頼哉) comes from Oarai Beach (大洗サンビーチ海水浴場), Ibaraki Prefecture.
